While Vardy's second booking has divided opinion, Roy Hodgson felt it was a harsh decision against the surprise league leader's top scorer.<img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2763806&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
