Day after winning Rio Olympics berth and first international gold, Dipa Karmakar talks about the road ahead.<img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2761249&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
