8221; Fabregas added.</p> <p>&#8220;That was the main reason why at the end he had to go. And for that, myself and all the team, will feel bad for him.&#8221;</p><img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2760775&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
