despite playing 900 minutes less than pair.</p> <p>&#8220;I think he is just behind Kane and Vardy so he is fighting to be the top scorer this year also,&#8221; Pellegrini said.</p> <p>&#8220;I am sure it will be difficult for the other strikers to keep up with his performances.&#8221;</p><img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2760709&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
