A PIL has been filed by former CBI Director R K Raghavan to restrain BCCI from effecting the deal with ICC that would hurt the board's revenue.<img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2760144&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
