Pakistan last May to play limited over games in Lahore and the tour was a big success for the PCB.</p><img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2760010&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
