David Warner strikes an unbeaten 90 off 59 balls to lead SRH to an emphatic seven-wicket win over defending champions MI.<img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2759539&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
