vered.</p> <p>Newcastle are three points from the safety zone and two behind north-east rivals Sunderland but with a gamne in hand over fourth-bottom Norwich City.</p><img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2759361&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
