Eugenson Lyngdoh and Seminlen Doungel scored for Bengaluru as Ashley Westwood's side took three points to clinch their second I-League title.<img alt="" border="0" src="http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=indianexpress.com&#038;blog=53855017&#038;post=2758017&#038;subd=indianexpressonline&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />
